// D = EXEC; EXEC = ~S0 & EXEC; SCC = (EXEC != 0).
// "ANDN1" = AND with NOT of operand 1 (S0).
// Sources (introduced in GFX9/Vega; B32 variant added in GFX10/RDNA):
//   vega-shader-instruction-set-architecture.pdf, page 115 (B64).
